	* Initial release

	Version 1.4.0
	########################################################################	
	Update manual
	Refactoring the code
	Fix bugs
	add extension configuration.
	 - you can set your own backgroundcolor
	 - you can turn on/off dividers2tabs
	 - you can set your own animation speed
	 - you can set your own images for the close and loadingimage
	 - you can set maxW and maxH for the clicked image size
	 - you can change stylesheets for a tag id for the closebutton
	 - if you use css styled content you can turn on/off the caption 